{
  "stem": "10835.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we were afraid of what they'll do to us as Jews once they catch us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, the Poles were more or less a little bit cocky.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they were confident that they'll be able to defy the German army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But as we all saw, they weren't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to a town called Sosnowiec, which was about 6 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We carried whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, we-- we went on trains, not real passenger trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went on these open--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--cargo trains, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and we went wherever we went, deeper into Poland, going east.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were planning to join the rest of-- of my father's relatives who lived in Kielce, where I was born.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we weren't able to get there, because we were being shot at from German planes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They did not throw bombs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were flying low and shooting from the planes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was-- we left on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we came to a little town called [INAUDIBLE], which was like between Myslowice and Kielce.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we-- we couldn't go any further.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we left the train, and we went into town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have-- we didn't know anybody to go to, so we slept like in the open fields.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the next morning, we were going to continue walking to Kielce.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But all of a sudden, from every corner, wherever you looked there were German soldiers approaching.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were there before us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, of course, we weren't able to continue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were able to return to Myslowice in three days, all of us except our father, because as we came closer, we met people who told us that all Jewish men were put into prison.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
